snippet.title: The Elder Scrolls: Castles - 20 Minutes of New Gameplay (Android) HD
snippet.description:
20 Minutes of No-Commentary gameplay on The Elder Scrolls: Castles which shadow-dropped for Android devices earlier today. This video was recorded on a Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra device.
